msgid "WMS LegendGraphic and Spacing groups"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_composer/composer_items/composer_legend.rst:224
msgid ""
"When you have added a WMS layer and you insert a legend item, a request "
"will be sent to the WMS server to provide a WMS legend. This Legend will "
"only be shown if the WMS server provides the GetLegendGraphic capability."
" The WMS legend content will be provided as a raster image."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_composer/composer_items/composer_legend.rst:229
msgid ""
":guilabel:`WMS LegendGraphic` is used to be able to adjust the "
":guilabel:`Legend width` and the :guilabel:`Legend height` of the WMS "
"legend raster image."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_composer/composer_items/composer_legend.rst:232
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Spacing` around title, groups, subgroups, symbols, labels, "
"boxes, columns and lines can be customized through this dialog."
msgstr ""

